## Summary

Sprint S-22 implemented HSM-backed cryptographic operations via HashiCorp Vault Transit engine and MFA-protected emergency kill switch. All 143 security tests pass with no critical, high, or medium severity vulnerabilities identified.

## Components Delivered

- VaultClient with AppRole authentication and auto-renewal
- KillSwitch with MFA protection and NATS broadcast
- MfaVerifier with TOTP implementation (RFC 6238)
- OAuthTokenEncryption for Discord tokens
- WalletVerification with challenge signing
- Prometheus metrics for all operations

## Security Verdict

Production-ready from a security perspective.
